<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.10">
<l>allal viḷaitta perumāṉai yāyar pāṭik kaṇiviḷakkai</l>
<l>villi putuvai nakarnampi viṭṭu cittaṉ viyaṉkōtai</l>
<l>villait tolaitta puruvattāḷ vēṭkai yuṟṟumika virumpum</l>
<l>collait tutikka vallārkaḷ tuṉpak kaṭaḷuḷ tuvaḷārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable of worshipping the words—that [express] the great love</l>
<l>Of she whose eyebrows finished off [the beauty of] a bow, the wonderful Kōtai,</l>
<l>[daughter of] Viṣṇucitta, the lord of the city of Villiputtūr,</l>
<l>Desiring the Lord who caused trouble, the beautiful Lamp of Gokula—</l>
<l>Will not be distressed in the ocean of sorrow!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
